\id 1PE - Dawro
\h 1 Phexiroosa
\toc3 1Ph
\toc2 1 Phexiroosa
\toc1 1 Phexiroosa
\mt1 Phexiroosi
\mt2 Xaafeedda Koyro Kiitaa
\imt1 Geluwaa
\ip Yesuusi kiitteedda Phexiroosi xaafeedda koyro kiitay xaafetteeddawe, he kiitaa giddon “Dooretteedda Xoossaa asatuwaa” geetettiide xeesettiyaanne Qeeri Iisiyan huuphissa bagga shaakuwan laaletteedda ammaniyaawanttussa. Ha kiitaa waanna qofay, ammanuwaa gaasuwan metuunne waayyii gakkeeddawantta minissanaassanne menthethanaassa. Xaafii hawaa oothiyaawe A hayquwaa, A dendduwaa, A laa7entho yuussaa odiyaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa nabbabiyaawantta hassayissiyaawaana. Unttunttu Yesuusi Kiristtoosa de7uwaa leemisuwaadan akkiide, metuwaa gencciide aadhdhanaadan hassayissee. Hawaanna ittippe gathiyaa wode, metuu unttunttu ammanuwaa xalttatethaa paacciyaawaanne Yesuusi Kiristtoosi qoncciyaa gallassi unttunttu bessiyaa gatiyaa akkanaw de7iyaawaa unttuntta hassayissee.
\ip Xaafii, unttunttu metuwan genccana mala menthethiyaawaa bollaakka, Kiristtoosa kaalliyaawanttu de7iyaawaadan unttunttu de7anaadan qofissee.
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatuwassi Imetteedda Qantha Qofatuwaa
\io1 Geluwaa (1:1-2)
\io1 Xoossaa ashshuwaabaa (1:3-12)
\io1 Geeyyeedda de7uwaa de7anaadan imetteedda maqquwaa (1:13-2:10)
\io1 Metuwaa wode ammaniyaa asay oothana bessiyaa aawotethaa (2:11-4:19)
\io1 Ammaniyaa asaa ashikketethaanne oosuwaa (5:1-11)
\io1 Wursethaa qutiyaa (5:12-14)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Taani, Yesuusi Kiristtoosi kiitteedda Phexiroosi, Xoossay dooreedda asatoo Phanxxoosa gadiyan, Galaatiyaa gadiyan, Qaphphadooqiyaa gadiyan, Iisiya biittiinininne Biitaaniyaa gadiyan betiyan de7iyaawanttoo dabidaabbiyaa xaafay.
\v 2 Yesuusi Kiristtoosaw hintte azazettana malanne A suuthan geeyyana mala, Xoossay Aawuu dooreedda hinttenttoo bare Ayyaanan geeshsheeddawanttoo, aadho keekatethaynne sarotethay gido.
\s1 De7uwaa Immana Geedda Hidootaa
\p 
\v 3 Nuuni Xoossaa, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa Aawuwaa, bare maarotethaa daruwaadankka nuuna laa7ethuwaa yeleeddawaa, Yesuusi Kiristtoosa hayiquwaappe dentheeddawaan nuussi de7uwaa hidootaa immeeddawaa galateetto.
\v 4 Qassi Xoossay hinttenttoo immana daro laatay wooqqennawe, bayennawenne dhayennawe saluwan naagee.
\v 5 Hewekka hinttenttussi, Xoossaa wolqqaan ammanuwan naagetti uttiide, atotethaw giigeeddawanttussi wurssethaa wodiyaan qonccanawaa.
\p 
\v 6 Ha77i guuthaa wodew haray atto dumma dumma paaciyaan hintte paacettanaw koshshooppekka, hawaan daro nashettite.
\v 7 Hewe haray atto, tamaan yeggina dhayiyaa worqqaappekka hintte ammanuu daro al77onne bali bayinnawaa gidiyaawaa bessanaassa; yaatiide Yesuusi Kiristtoosi beettiyaa wode, galataa, bonchchuwaanne sabaa hintte akkana.
\v 8-9 Hintte A erana dhayooppekka, siiqiita; hintte ha77i A be7ana dhayooppekka, ammaniita. Qassi hintte hintte ammanoo polo gidiyaa hintte shemppuwaa atotethaa akkiya diraw, odanaw danddayettenna bonchchuu kumeedda nashechchaa nashettiita.
\p 
\v 10 Xoossay hinttenttoo immana aadho keekatethaabaw timbbitiyaa odeedda nabatuu loythi biddiide, ha atotethaabaa koyyeeddino.
\v 11 Unttunttun de7iya Kiristtoosa Ayyaanay Kiristtoosa tuggaabaanne hewaappe guyyiyan yaana bonchchuwaabaa kasetiide markkattiidde, awude woy waaneedda wodiyaan yaanenttonne akeekisseeddawaadan, unttunttu koyyeeddino.
\v 12 He timbbitiyaa odiyaawanttu ootheedda oosuu hinttessappe attin, unttunttu huuphiyaassa gidennawaa Xoossay unttunttoo qonccisseedda; ha77i hintte siseedda mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa hinttenttoo odeedda asatuu, barew saluwaappe kiitetteedda Geeshsha Ayyaanaa wolqqan odeeddino. Hewaa kiitanchchatuukka be7anaw amottiino.
\s1 Geeshshatethan De7iyaawaa
\p 
\v 13 Hewaa diraw, oosuwaa oothanaw hintte wozanaan qofaa giigissiidde hintte huuphiya naagite. Yesuusi Kiristtoosi qoncciyaa wode aadho keekatethaa hintte akkiya diraw, kumentha hidootaan naagite.
\v 14 Xoossaw azazettiyaa naanaadan; hintte kase erennaan amotteedda amuwaa kaalloppite.
\v 15-16 Shin hinttena xeeseedda Xoossay geeshsha gideeddawaadan, hinttekka hintte oosuwaa ubbaan geeshsha gidite. Xoossaa Maxaafan, “Taani geeshsha gidiyaa diraw, hinttekka geeshsha gidite” geetettiide xaafetteedda. \x - \xo 1:15-16 \xt Wog 11:44-45; 19:2\x*
\p 
\v 17 Asaa huuphiyan huuphiyan deemuwaa xeellennan A oosuwaadan pirddiyaa Xoossaa woossiidde hintte, “Nu Aabboo” giide A xeesiyaawaa gidooppe, ha alamiyaan bete gidiide hintte de7iya wodiyaan yashshatethaan de7ite.
\v 18-19 Hintte hintte aawatuwappe laatteedda pathenna de7uwaappe wozetteeddawe, dhayiyaa biraa woy worqqaa malaana gidennawaa eriita; borissiyaabay woy qitay bayinna dorssaa suuthaadan, al77o Kiristtoosa suuthan hintte wozetteeddita.
\v 20 Xoossay sa7ay medhettanaappe kase Kiristtoosa doori wotheedda; shin hintte diraw, ha wodiyaa wurssethaan I beetteedda.
\v 21 Hintte ammanuunne hintte akkana giide nashechchan naagi utteeddabay Xoossaan de7ana mala, Xoossay hayiquwaappe A denthiide, aw bonchchuwaa immeeddawaa aani ammaniita.
\p 
\v 22 Tumatethaw hintte azazettiyaawan, lo77a malatiyaa iitatethay bayinnaan hintte ishatuwaa siiqanaw hintte huuphiyaa geeshshiide, ittuu ittuwaanna minissiide wozanaappe siiqettite.
\p 
\v 23 Hintte hayiqqiyaa zerethaappe laa7enthuwaa yelettibeykkita; shin medhinaw de7iyaawaanne sinthawukka de7ana Xoossaa qaalaan hayqqenna zerethaappe yeletteeddita.
\v 24 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Asay ubbay maataa mala; A bonchchuu ubbayikka maataa ciishshaa mala. Maatay melee; ciishshayikka qoqqofettee. \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Isa 40:6-8\x*
\v 25 Shin Godaa qaalay medhinaw de7ee” yaage. Hawe hinttenttoo Goday odeedda mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa.
\c 2
\s1 De7uwaa Shuchchaanne Geeshsha Asaa
\p 
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, hintteppe iitatethaa ubbaa, cimmiyaawaa ubbaa, lo77a malatiyaa iitatethaa, qanaatiyaanne zigirssaa ubbaa diggite.
\v 2-3 Goday keeka gideeddawaa hintte de7uwan be7eeddawaa gidooppe, ha77i yeletteedda gacino naanatuwaadan, ushiidde diccanawunne attanaw xillo gideedda ayyaanaa maathaa laamotite. \x - \xo 2:2-3 \xt Maz 34:8\x*
\p 
\v 4 Godaakko de7o shuchchaakko shiiqite. Asay A ixxeedda; shin Xoossaa matan I dooretteedda al77o.
\v 5 Hinttekka qassi de7o shuchchaadan, geeshsha qeesaa gidiide, Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna Xoossaa nashechchiyaa ayyaanaa yarshshuwaa Xoossaw yarshshanaw, hintte hintte huuphew ayyaana keethaadan keexettite.
\v 6 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Be7ite, taani Xiyoone giya katamaan golliyaa godaa xaphuwaa minissiyaa, dooretteedda, al77o shuchchaa wothay; aani ammaniyaa ooninne yeellatenna” yaage. \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Isa 28:16\x*
\v 7 Hewaa diraw, ha shuchchay hinttenttoo ammaniyaawanttoo daro al77a; shin ammanennawanttoo, “Gimbbiyaawanttu kadheedda shuchchay godaa xaphuwaa minissiyaa, ubbaappe aadhdhiyaa shuchchaa gideedda” yaage.
\v 8 Qassikka, “Ha shuchchay asaa dhubbiyaa shuchchaanne asaa kunddissiyaa zaallaa” yaage; unttunttu Xoossaa qaalaa ammanenna diraw, unttunttoo kassenna qofetteeddawaadan dhubetteeddino. \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Isa 8:14-15\x*
\p 
\v 9 Shin Xoossay dhumaappe maalalissiyaa bare poo7oo hinttena xeeseedda; hintte A ooratha oosuwaa odanaw dooretteedda zare; hintte kaatiyaa qeesatuwaa; geeshsha asanne Xoossaassi buzo asa. \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Kes 19:5-6; Isa 43:20,21; Zar 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; Tit 2:14; Isa 9:2\x*
\v 10 Hintte kase Xoossaa asa gidikkita; shin ha77i hintte A asa; hintte kase maarotethaa akkibeykkita; shin ha77i maarotethaa akkeeddita. \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Hos 2:23\x*
\s1 Xoossaa Ayllatuwaa
\p 
\v 11 Ta dabbatoo, hintte ha sa7an imathaanne bete gidiide de7iyaawantta gideeddawaadan, ubba wode hintte shemppuwaanna olettiyaa asatethaa amuwaappe hintte haakkana mala, taani hinttena woossay.
\v 12 Amenenna asay hinttena iitabaa oothiyaawanttudan zigiriyaa wode, Kiristtoosi yiyaa gallassi hintte lo77o oosuwaa unttunttu akeekiide, Xoossaa galatana mala, hintte de7uwaa unttunttu giddon loythi naagite.
\p 
\v 13 Godaa diraw, asaa higgiyaa ubbaw moodettite; kaatiikka ubbaappe bolla gidiyaa diraw, aw moodettite.
\v 14 Qassi gadiyaa mooddiyaawanttookka moodettite. Ayissi gooppe, unttunttu iitabaa oothiyaawantta muranawunne lo77obaa oothiyaawantta galatanaw kaatiyaappe kiitetteeddino.
\v 15 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay hintte hintte lo77o oosuwan kadhiyaa eeyaa asatuwaa haasayaa co77u udanawaa koyyee.
\v 16 Aylletethaappe kesiide, Xoossaa ayilliyaadan de7iteppe attin, he ayilletethaappe keseeddawaa iitatethaa genthiyaawaa oothoppite.
\v 17 Asaa ubbaa bonchchite. Hintte ishatuwaa siiqite. Xoossaw yayyite. Kaatiyaa bonchchite.
\s1 Kiristtoosa Gakkeedda Metuwaa Leemisuwaa
\p 
\v 18 Ayllatoo, hintte lo77o godatuwaa xalalawunne ashikke godatuwaa xalalaw gidennaan, iitatookka daro yayyiide moodettite.
\v 19 Ayissi gooppe, asay naaqqiyaa wode waayyettiyaa uray Xoossaa qoppiidde, oge baynnaan naaqettooppe Xoossay A anjjana.
\v 20 Ayissi gooppe, hintte nagaraa oothina, hinttena dechchiya wode, hintte danddayooppe, hinttenttoo ay galatay de7ii? Shin lo77obaa oothiide waayyiyaa hintte danddayooppe, Xoossay hinttena hewoo anjjana.
\v 21 Xoossay hinttena xeeseeddawe hewaa diraassa; ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosi hinttenttoo waayyettee; hintte A qatamaa kaallana mala, hinttenttoo leemisuwaa gideedda.
\v 22 Nagaraa I oothibeenna; bare doonaappe wordduwaa haasayibeenna. \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Isa 53:9\x*
\v 23 Asay barena boriyaa wode, zaariide boribeenna; waayyettiyaa wodekka manddibeenna. Shin xilluwaa pirddiyaa Xoossaw barena aathiide immeedda. \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Isa 53:7\x*
\v 24 Nuuni nagaraw hayiqqiide, xillotethaw de7ana mala, Kiristtoosi bare huuphew bare ashuwan nu nagaraa masqqaliyan tookkeedda; hintte A maythaan paxeeddita. \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Isa 53:5\x*
\v 25 Ayissi gooppe, hintte ogi baleedda dorssaa mala; shin ha77i hintte shemppuwaa heemmiyaawaakkonne naagiyaawaakko simmeedita. \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Isa 53:6\x*
\c 3
\s1 Asinaawaanne Machchiyaawaa
\p 
\v 1-2 Hewaadankka machchetoo, hintte asinatuwaappe Xoossaa qaalaw azazettenna ittuu ittuu de7ooppekka, hintte palumettennan, unttunttu hintte yashshatethaanne hintte geeshsha de7uwaa be7iide xoonettana mala, unttunttoo moodettite.
\v 3 Hintte hintte huuphiyaa al77o baan giigissiyaawaaninne worqqaa wothiyaawan woy al77o mayuwaa mayiyaawan hinttenttu bolla baggaa loythoppite.
\v 4 Shin hintte garssan qosetteedda asatethaa lo77otethay Xoossaa sinthan hinttenttoo daro al77o gidiide, dhayenna ashikkenne woppu geedda ayyaanaa gido.
\v 5 Ayissi gooppe, hewaadan Xoossaan hidooteedda geeshsha macca asatuu beni wode barenttu asinaw moodettiide, barentta daro loytheeddino.
\v 6 Hewaadan Saara Abraahaama, “Ta godaw” yaaga xeesaadde, aw azazettaaddu; hinttekka ittibawunne yayyennaan lo77obaa oothooppe, I naanatuwaa. \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Dom 18:12\x*
\p 
\v 7 Hewaadan asinatoo, hintte macca asatuwaanna akeekan ittippe de7ite. Unttunttoo daaburanchcha asatethay de7iyaa diraw, unttuntta bonchchite; hintte woosay dhubettenna mala, Xoossay immeedda de7uwaa aadho keekatethaa unttunttu hinttenanna ittippe laattino.
\s1 Lo77obaa Oothiidde Metuwaa Akkiyawaa
\p 
\v 8 Wurssethaan, ubbay itti qofaan de7ite. Ittuu ittoo qarettite; ishatuwaadan siiqettite; qassi ittuu ittoo keekiyaawanttanne hintte huuphiyaa kawushshiyaawantta gidite.
\v 9 Iitaa diraw iitaa woy sheqaa diraw sheqaa zaaroppite; hewaa aggiide, Xoossay hinttenttu anjjuwaa laattanaadan hinttena xeeseedda diraw, anjjite.
\v 10 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay hawaadan yaage; “De7uwaa dosiyaawenne lo77o gallassaa be7anaw koyyiyaawe oona gidooppenne bare inxxarssan iitabaa haasayiyaawaanne wordduwaa odiyaawaa aggo. \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Maz 34:12-16\x*
\p 
\v 11 “Iitabaa oothiyaawaa aggiide, lo77obaa ootho; sarotethaakka loythi koyyonne kaallanaw baaxeto.
\p 
\v 12 “Ayissi gooppe, Godaa ayfii xillotuwaakko xeellee; qassi A haythay ubba wode unttunttu woosaw dooya de7ee. Shin Goday iitabaa oothiyaawantta bare hanqquwaa som77iyaan xeellee” yaage.
\p 
\v 13 Hintte lo77obaa oothanaw amottooppe, hinttena qohanawe oonee?
\v 14 Shin haray atto, xillotethaa diraw hintte waayyettooppekka, anjjetteeddawantta. Asaw yayyoppitenne hirggoppite. \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Mat 5:10; Isa 8:12-13\x*
\v 15 Shin Kiristtoosa hintte wozanaan bonchchitenne A hintte Godaa oothite. Xoossay hinttenttoo hidooteedda de7uwaassi gaasuwaa oochchiyaa oossinne zaaruwaa immanaw ubba wode giigi uttite;
\v 16 shin hewaa ashikketethaaninne yashshatethaan oothite. Qassi Kiristtoosan hintte de7iya lo77o de7uwaa iitabaa ootheeddawaadan, hintte bollan iitabaa haasayiyaa asay bare zigiriyaawan yeellatana mala, hintte wozanay geeshsha gido.
\v 17 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay geeddawaa gidooppe, iitabaa ootheedda diraw waayyettiyaawaappe, lo77obaa ootheedda diraw waayyettiyaawe keeka.
\v 18 Ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosi nuuna Xoossaakko afanaw, barew xillo gidiidde, makkalanchchatuwaa diraw, itti gede ubbaa nagaraw hayiqqeedda; I bare asatethan hayiqqeedda; shin ayyaanan paxeedda.
\v 19 Qassi he Ayyaanan, qashuwan de7iya ayyaanatuwaakko biide, unttunttoo qaalaa odeedda.
\v 20 He ayyaanatuu amareedda, hosppun asatuu haathaan atteedda markkabiyaa Nohe keexxishshin, Xoossay danddayiide gami77eedda wode, Xoossaw azazettibeenna asaa ayyaanatuwaa. \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Dom 6:1–7:24\x*
\v 21 Hewe xinqqataw leemisuwaa gidiide, hinttena ha77i ashshee; suure wozanaappe Xoossaa woossiyaawaappe attin, bollaa qitaa meecciyaawaa gidenna; hewe hinttena Yesuusi Kiristtoosi hayiquwaappe denddeeddawaan ashshee.
\v 22 Saluwaa biide Xoossaappe ushechcha baggan I uttiide, kiitanchchaa ubbaa, maataanna de7iyaawanttanne wolqqaamatuwaa mooddee.
\c 4
\s1 Geeshshatethan De7ana De7uwaabaa
\p 
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, Kiristtoosi bare ashuwan nuussi waayyetteedda diraw, hinttekka he qofaan danccettite. Ayissi gooppe, bare ashuwan waayyetteedda uray nagaraa oothiyaawaa aggeedda.
\v 2 Hawaappe sinthan, ha sa7an shemppuwaanna de7anaw atteedda wodiyaan, Xoossay koyyiyaawaadan de7anaw bessiyaawaappe attin, asaa amuwaadan de7anaw bessenna.
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, ammanenna asay oothanaw dosiyaawaa hintte oothiidde, woshummanaw kajjeeliyaawaan, amuwan, mathuwan, yethaan, ushshaan, pokkiyaa eeqaw goyinniyaawan, de7eedda kase aadhdheedda wodii hinttenttoo gidanawa.
\v 4 Ammanenna asaanna hintte shoray bayinna oosuwaa ittippe oothenna diraw maalalettiide, hinttena boriino.
\v 5 Shin unttunttu paxa de7iya asaa bollanne hayqqeedda asaa bolla pirddanaw giigi utteedda Xoossaw zaaruwaa immana.
\v 6 Hayqqeedda asay \f + \fr 4:6 \fq Hayqqeedda asay: \ft Yesuusa ammananaappe kasenna hayqqeeddawantta woy Nohe wode asatuwaa. 3:19 xeellite.\f* bare asatethan asay pirddettiyaawadan pirddettanawunne qassi ayyaanan Xoossay de7iyaawaadan de7anaw, wonggalaa mishiraachchuu unttunttoo hewoo odetteedda.
\s1 Xoossay Immeedda Imotatuwaa Loythi Ayissiyaawaa
\p 
\v 7 Ubbabawukka wurssethay matatteedda. Hewaa diraw, Xoossaa woossanaw qofaan geeyyiide, hinttena naagitenne minnite.
\v 8 Siiquu daro nagaraa kammiyaa diraw, ubbabaappe aathiide ittuu ittuwaanna wozanaappe siiqettite. \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Lem 10:12\x*
\v 9 Zuuzummennan ittuu ittuwaa imathatethaan mokkite.
\v 10 Hintte huuphiyan huuphiyan Xoossaappe dumma dumma aadho keekatethaa akkeeddawaadankka, Xoossaa dumma imuwaa hadaraa loythi kesiyaawanttudan, ittuu ittoo oothite.
\v 11 Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna ubbabaani Xoossay galatettana mala, ooninne odiyaawaa gidooppe, qaalaa Xoossaappe akkiide odiyaawaadan odo. Qassi ooninne maaddiyaawaa gidooppe, Xoossay aw immiya wolqqan maaddo. Bonchchuunne godatethay Xoossaassi medhinaappe medhinaw gido. Amen77i.
\s1 Metuwaa Wode Minniyaawaa
\p 
\v 12 Ta siiqatoo, hintte giddon tamaadan guuddiidde paacciyaa waayyii yiyaawaa oorathabay haniyaawaadan malalettoppite.
\v 13 Shin Kiristtoosa bonchchuu beettiyaa wode hintte nashettana mala, aananna waayyettiyaawan nashetite.
\v 14 Asay hinttena Kiristtoosa sunthaa diraw boriyaawaa gidooppe, hintte anjjetteeddawantta; ayissi gooppe, bonchcho Ayyaanay, Xoossaa Ayyaanay, hintte bolla shemppana.
\v 15 Hintteppe ooninne shemppuwaa wodheeddawaadan, woy kayisuwaadan, woy iitabaa ootheedda asaadan, woy hara asaa yewuwaa geleeddawaadan waayyettoppo.
\v 16 Shin ooninne Kiristtaaniyaa gidiyaa diraw waayyettooppe, Kiristtoosa sunthaa diraw, Xoossaa galatanaappe attin, yeellatoppo.
\p 
\v 17 Ayissi gooppe, pirdday Xoossaa golliyan doomettiyaa wodii gakkeedda. Qassi he pirdday koyiro nu bolla doomettiyaawaa gidooppe, A wonggalaw azazettennawanttu wurssethay ayaa gidanee?
\v 18 Xillo asay tuggaan attiyaawaa gidooppe, makkalanchchaynne nagaranchchay yaatina waananee? \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Lem 11:31\x*
\v 19 Hewaa diraw qassi, Xoossay geeddawaadan waayyettiyaawanttu lo77obaa oothiidde, barenttu shemppuwaa hadaraa barena medhdheedda ammanettiya Xoossaw immino.
\c 5
\s1 Xoossaa Asaa Ayissanaw Imetteedda Zoriyaa
\p 
\v 1 Simmi taani woosa golliyaa cimatuwaanna cima gidiyaawenne, Kiristtoosa waayyiyaa markkattiyaawe, qassi qonccana bonchchuwaa shaakkanawe hintte giddon de7iya cimatuwaa zoray.
\v 2 Hintte giddon de7iya Xoossaa wudiyaa Xoossay koyyiyaawaadan heemmite. Dosuwaanappe attin, wolqqan gidenna. Qassi hintte go77a xalalaa xeellennan, lo77o qofaan heemmite.
\v 3 Wudew hintte leemisuwaa giditeppe attin, hintte heemmiyaawantta wolqqaan heemmoppite.
\v 4 Qassi heemmiyaawanttu kaappuu qoncciyaa wode, bayenna bonchcho akililiyaa hintte akkana.
\p 
\v 5 Hewaadankka yalaga asatoo, cimatoo moodettite. Ubbaykka ittuu ittoo oothanaw hintte huuphiyaa kawushshiyaawaa afilaadan mayyite. Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay otorettiyaawantta ixxee; shin barena kawushshiyaawanttoo aadho keekatethaa immee. \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Lem 3:34\x*
\v 6 Xoossay bare lo77o wodiyaan hinttena dhoqqu oothana mala, wolqqaama Xoossaa kushiyaappe garssanna hinttena toochchite.
\v 7 I hinttenttoo qoppiyaa diraw, hinttena hirggissiyaa ubbabaa A bolla olite.
\p 
\v 8 Xalahiyaa kaappuu, hintte morkkii, mittiyaa uraa koyyiide, gudiyaa gaammuwaadan hintte yuushshuwan yuuyyiyaa diraw naagettitenne beegottite.
\v 9 Sa7an de7iya hintte ishatuu hewaadan waayyettiyaawaa eriide, ammanuwan minniide, aananna eqettite.
\v 10 Aadho keekatethaa ubbaa Xoossay, bare medhinaa bonchchoo Kiristtoosi Yesuusa bagganna hinttena xeeseeddawe, amareedda wodiyaa hintte waayyetteeddawaappe guyyiyan, I bare huuphew hinttena shiri orathananne minissana. Qassi I hinttena maaddananne baasi essana.
\v 11 Wolqqay medhinaappe medhinaa gakkanaw aw gido. Amen77i.
\s1 Wurssetha Sarotaa
\p 
\v 12 Hawe Xoossaa tumu aadho keekatethaa gidiyaawaa taani hinttenttoo markkattaaddenne hinttena zoraadde, hinttenttoo qanthaan xaafeedda dabidaabbiyaa ammanettiya ishaa gaade taani qoppiyaa Sillaase bolla kiittaaddi; he aadho keekatethan minneeddita.
\p 
\v 13 Hinttenana ittippe dooretteedda Baabiloonen \f + \fr 5:13 \fq Baabiloone: \ft Saxaa Maxaafaa qofaadan, ha sunthay Roome guussaa gidennaan aggenna.\f* de7iya woosa golliyaa asaynne ta na7ay Marqqoossi hinttena “Saro saro” giino.
\v 14 Siiquwaa yeretaa yerettiidde, ittuu ittuwaa sarotite.
\p Hinttew, Kiristtoosanna ittuwaa gideeddawanttoo ubbatuwaassi sarotethay gido. Amen77i.
